,(2973,104,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(2974,104,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>POČNITE DRUGU FAZU:</strong>\r\nInox spahtlom uklonite višak materijala.\r\nBRUŠENJE:\r\nOPCIJA 1:\r\nRučno brušenje brusnim sunđerom granulacije 180.\r\nOPCIJA 2:\r\nMašinsko brušenje brusnim diskom od 180 zrna.\r\nSavršeno izbrisite površinu.\r\nNanesite CeboMarmo Bianco na prvi sloj i na vene poštujući smer obrade.\r\nNanesite CeboMarmo Bianco na prvi sloj i na vene poštujući smer obrade.'),(2975,104,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(2976,104,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f','310'),(2977,104,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(2978,104,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s','311'),(2979,104,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(2980,104,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','Nanesite obojeni CeboMarmo čeličnom lopaticom na istu porvšinu i na okolnu površinu, pritiskajući odgovarajući pritisak.\r\nNanesite još jedan sloj CeboMarmo Bianco da istaknete vene, pritiskajući veći pritisak.\r\nPonovite operaciju za druge vene.\r\n\r\n<strong>MOLIM OBRATITE PAŽNJU:</strong>\r\nNastavite tako što ćete raditi jednu po jednu venu.'),(2981,104,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(2982,104,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_f','312'),(2983,104,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(2984,104,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_s','313'),(2985,104,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(2986,104,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_text','<strong>POLIRANJE:</strong>\r\n\r\nOPCIJA 1 - Ručno poliranje:\r\nPre potpunog sušenja, polirajte površinu više puta prolazeći čist inox gletericom, pritiskajući odgovarajući pritisak.\r\n\r\nOPCIJA 2 - Mašinsko poliranje -:\r\nNakon najmanje 2-4 sata od nanošenja poslednjeg sloja CeboMarma, poliranje izvedite abrazivnim diskovima u nizu:\r\n1. zrno 1.000\r\n2. zrno 2.000\r\n3 ° Zrno 4.000\r\n\r\n<strong>NAPOMENA:</strong> Nakon mašinskog poliranja i dalje je potrebno ručno poliranje Inox gletaricom.'),(2987,104,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(2988,104,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_image_f','314'),(2989,104,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(2990,104,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_image_s',''),(2991,104,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(2992,104,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_text','Za još realističniji efekat mermera, moguće je bolje definisati gravure prelaskom preko CeboMarmo Bianco -a, razblaženog vodom i nanešenog četkicom.'),(2993,104,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(2994,104,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','4'),(2995,104,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(2996,104,'instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','Treca i poslednja faza'),(2997,104,'_instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(2998,104,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','315'),(2999,104,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(3000,104,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','316'),(3001,104,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(3002,104,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>ZAŠTITA I KONAČNO POLIRANJE:</strong>\r\nCeboVax: završna obrada za unutrašnjost na bazi pčelinjeg voska, prozračna i vodoodbojna.\r\nNanesite sloj CeboVak -a razblažen 1: 1 sa vodom, koristeći sintetički sunđer. Nanesite vosak prateći smer obrade: odmah zatim mekom krpom pređite preko površine da biste uklonili višak voska.\r\n\r\nSačekajte 10-15 minuta i ispolirajte površinu više puta prolazeći kroz savršeno čistu inox gletericu, pritiskajući odgovarajući pritisak.'),(3003,104,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(3004,104,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','1'),(3005,104,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(3006,104,'_oembed_7d9efc11ee478a5b713e0bf3c8851470','{{unknown}}'),(3007,317,'_wp_attached_file','2021/10/Cebos_S.A._CeboMarmo_Pietra_Imperiale.pdf'),(3008,318,'_wp_attached_file','2021/10/S.T.-CEBOMARMO.pdf'),(3009,319,'_wp_attached_file','2021/10/IT_S_S_-04_049_CLP_1-CEBOMARMO.pdf'),(3010,320,'_wp_attached_file','2021/10/cebomarmo_catalogo_web.pdf'),(3011,104,'add_video_link','a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:22:\"Pietra Imperiale Video\";s:3:\"url\";s:113:\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DsDBfg9aXsE&list=PLnBmYKHwQhA3X5g_8bG0lG5qfPYq_KwwX&index=3&ab_channel=CebosColor\";s:6:\"target\";s:6:\"_blank\";}'),(3012,104,'_add_video_link','field_6175500f7b773'),(3015,330,'_wp_old_slug','1_email_1-2'),(3016,104,'half_section_f',''),(3017,104,'_half_section_f','field_61771b4aae9d1'),(3018,104,'half_section_s',''),(3019,104,'_half_section_s','field_61771b6cae9d2'),(3020,344,'_wp_attached_file','2021/10/zidne-dekoracije-slika-katalog-sekcija.jpg'),(3021,344,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:1920;s:6:\"height\";i:745;s:4:\"file\";s:50:\"2021/10/zidne-dekoracije-slika-katalog-sek