ption','PIETRA NOBILE - PLEMENITI KAMEN\r\n\r\nCeboMarmo, sjajno kamenje\r\n\r\nDragocena akrilna završna obrada na vodenoj bazi, sa sjajnim izgledom. CeboMarmo reinterpretira mermerni efekat reprodukujući pokrete tipičnih žila i sjaj dragocenog i prefinjenog materijala, dajući ekskluzivni šarm svakom okruženju.'),(4361,475,'_page_main_content_description','field_6175355dc93bd'),(4362,475,'order_product_description',''),(4363,475,'_order_product_description','field_61753591c93be'),(4364,475,'instructions_section_title','Uputstvo za upotrebu'),(4365,475,'_instructions_section_title','field_61753bffa8575'),(4366,475,'instructions_section_description','Pogodni mediji:\r\n\r\nZidovi moraju biti savršeno glatki i ravni: sve nedostatke treba ukloniti. U suprotnom bi se prilikom primene CeboMarma mogli uočiti nedostaci.\r\n\r\nAko je potrebno gletovanje, preporučuje se da nastavite poštujući smer i način primene izabranog efekta.\r\n\r\nU prisustvu glatkih, krečnih ili upijajućih podloga, četkom nanesite sloj CeboFik M fiksatora razblaženog 1: 1 sa vodom.'),(4367,475,'_instructions_section_description','field_61753c63a8576'),(4368,475,'instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','Prva faza'),(4369,475,'_instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(4370,475,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','481'),(4371,475,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4372,475,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','461'),(4373,475,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4374,475,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>Primena CeboFik Primo:</strong>\r\nNanesite CeboFik Primo u jednom sloju, sa kratkodlakim valjkom, razblaženim 20% vodom i sačekajte potpuno sušenje (6-8 sati).\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),(4375,475,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4376,475,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f','482'),(4377,475,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4378,475,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s',''),(4379,475,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4380,475,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','CeboMarmo aplikacija, PLEMENITI KAMEN\r\nNanesite CeboMarmo tamnu boju inox gletericom, dijagonalno po celoj površini.\r\n\r\n<strong>ZAVRŠETAK PRVE FAZE:</strong>\r\nSačekajte potpuno sušenje (najmanje 6-8 sati).'),(4381,475,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4382,475,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','2'),(4383,475,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(4384,475,'instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','Druga faza'),(4385,475,'_instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(4386,475,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','483'),(4387,475,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4388,475,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','484'),(4389,475,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4390,475,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','Uklonite sve nedostatke i, ako je potrebno, ručno ili mašinski izbrusite brusnim papirom granulacije 180.\r\nNanesite CeboMarmo tamnu boju čeličnom gletericom, dijagonalno. Da bi se sprečilo da se proizvod osuši pre nego što se preklapa svetla boja, preporučuje se da nastavite sa izradom zida za oko 2 kvadratna metra odjednom.'),(4391,475,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4392,475,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f','484'),(4393,475,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4394,475,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s','485'),(4395,475,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4396,475,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','Na još svež proizvod nanesite svetlu boju CeboMarmo poštujući smer obrade.\r\nPređite sa inox gletericom koja vrši odgovarajući pritisak da ujednači i zbije proizvod.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ponovite postupak po celoj površini.</span>'),(4397,475,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4398,475,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','2'),(4399,475,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(4400,475,'instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','Poliranje'),(4401,475,'_instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(4402,475,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','486'),(4403,475,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4404,475,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','487'),(4405,475,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4406,475,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>OPCIJA 1</strong> - Ručno poliranje -:\r\nPre potpunog sušenja polirajte površinu savršeno čistom inox gletericom.\r\n\r\n<strong>OPCIJA 2</strong> - Mašinsko poliranje -:\r\nNakon najmanje 2-4 sata od nanošenja poslednjeg sloja CeboMarma, poliranje izvedite abrazivnim diskovima u nizu:\r\n1. zrno 2.000\r\n2. zrno 4.000\r\n<strong>NAPOMENA:</strong> Nakon mašinskog poliranja i dalje je potrebno ručno poliranje inox gletericom.'),(4407,475,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4408,475,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','1'),(4409,475,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(4410,475,'instructions_stages_3_instruction_label_title','Zaštita i konačno poliranje'),(4411,475,'_instructions_stages_3_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(4412,475,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','488'),(4413,475,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4414,475,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','316'),(4415,475,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4416,475,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','CeboVax: završna obrada za unutrašnjost na bazi pčelinjeg voska, prozračna i vodoodbojna.\r\nNanesite sloj CeboVax -a razblažen 1: 1 sa vodom, koristeći sintetički sundjer. Nanesite vosak prateći smer obrade: odmah zatim mekom krpom pređite preko površine da biste uklonili višak voska.\r\nSačekajte 10-15 minuta i ispolirajte površinu više puta prolazeći savršeno čistom inox gletericom, pritiskajući odgovarajući pritisak.\r\nPIETRA NOBILE se takođe može napraviti u VERTIKALNOM pravcu, prateći iste metode nanošenja, jednostavno promenom smera obrade.'),(4417,475,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4418,475,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details','1'),(4419,475,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(4420,475,'instructions_stages','4'),(4421,475,'_instructions_stages','field_61753c82a8577'),(4422,475,'half_section_f',''),(4423,475,'_half_section_f','field_61771b4aae9d1'),(4424,475,'half_section_s',''),(4425,475,'_half_section_s','field_61771b6cae9d2'),(4426,475,'background_ima