gle_slider_image','field_61753531c93bc'),(4477,493,'page_slider_images_2_single_slider_image','496'),(4478,493,'_page_slider_images_2_single_slider_image','field_61753531c93bc'),(4479,493,'page_slider_images_3_single_slider_image','497'),(4480,493,'_page_slider_images_3_single_slider_image','field_61753531c93bc'),(4481,493,'page_slider_images','4'),(4482,493,'_page_slider_images','field_617534efc93bb'),(4483,493,'page_main_content_description','PIETRA RINASCIMENTALE - RENESANSKI KAMEN\r\n\r\nCeboMarmo, sjajno kamenje\r\n\r\nDragocena akrilna završna obrada na vodenoj bazi, sa sjajnim izgledom. CeboMarmo reinterpretira mermerni efekat reprodukujući pokrete tipičnih žila i sjaj dragocenog i prefinjenog materijala, dajući ekskluzivni šarm svakom okruženju.'),(4484,493,'_page_main_content_description','field_6175355dc93bd'),(4485,493,'order_product_description',''),(4486,493,'_order_product_description','field_61753591c93be'),(4487,493,'instructions_section_title','Uputstvo za upotrebu'),(4488,493,'_instructions_section_title','field_61753bffa8575'),(4489,493,'instructions_section_description','Pogodni mediji:\r\n\r\nZidovi moraju biti savršeno glatki i ravni: sve nedostatke treba ukloniti. U suprotnom bi se prilikom primene CeboMarma mogli uočiti nedostaci podloge.\r\n\r\nAko je potrebno gletovanje , preporučuje se da nastavite poštujući smer i način primene izabranog efekta.\r\n\r\nU prisustvu glatkih, krečnih ili upijajućih podloga, četkom nanesite sloj CeboFik M fiksatora razblaženog 1: 1 sa vodom.'),(4490,493,'_instructions_section_description','field_61753c63a8576'),(4491,493,'instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','Prva faza'),(4492,493,'_instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(4493,493,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','461'),(4494,493,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4495,493,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','498'),(4496,493,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4497,493,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>Primena CeboFix Primo:</strong>\r\nNanesite CeboFix Primo u jednom sloju, sa kratkodlakim valjkom, razblaženim 20% vodom i sačekajte potpuno sušenje (6-8 sati).\r\n\r\nCeboMarmo aplikacija, RENESANSNI KAMEN\r\nNanesite CeboMarmo Bianco inox gletericom, dijagonalno. Da se ​​proizvod ne bi osušio pre nego što se preklapaju druge boje, preporučuje se da nastavite sa nanošenjem na oko 2 kvadratna metra odjednom.'),(4498,493,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4499,493,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f','499'),(4500,493,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4501,493,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s','500'),(4502,493,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4503,493,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','Na još svež proizvod nanesite ostale boje CeboMarma, jednu po jednu, uvek poštujući smer obrade.\r\nPonovite postupak po celoj površini.\r\n\r\n<strong>ZAVRŠETAK PRVE FAZE:</strong>\r\nSačekajte potpuno sušenje (najmanje 6-8 sati).'),(4504,493,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4505,493,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','2'),(4506,493,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(4507,493,'instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','Druga faza'),(4508,493,'_instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(4509,493,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','501'),(4510,493,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4511,493,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(4512,493,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4513,493,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','Uklonite sve nedostatke i, ako je potrebno, ručno ili mašinski izbrusite brusnim papirom granulacije 180.\r\nNanesite CeboMarmo Bianco inox gletericom po celoj površini, poštujući smer obrade. Pređite sa odgovarajućim pritiskom da kompaktirate i ujednačite proizvod.'),(4514,493,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4515,493,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','1'),(4516,493,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(4517,493,'instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','Poliranje'),(4518,493,'_instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(4519,493,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','502'),(4520,493,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4521,493,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','503'),(4522,493,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4523,493,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>OPCIJA 1</strong> - Ručno poliranje -:\r\nPre potpunog sušenja, polirajte površinu više puta prolazeći čistom inox gletericom, pritiskajući odgovarajući pritisak.\r\n\r\n<strong>OPCIJA 2</strong> - Mašinsko poliranje -:\r\nNakon najmanje 2-4 sata od nanošenja poslednjeg sloja CeboMarma, poliranje izvedite abrazivnim diskovima u nizu:\r\n1. zrno 2.000\r\n2. zrno 4.000\r\n<strong>NAPOMENA:</strong> Nakon mašinskog poliranja i dalje je potrebno ručno poliranje inox gletericom.'),(4524,493,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4525,493,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','1'),(4526,493,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(4527,493,'instructions_stages_3_instruction_label_title','Zaštita i konačno poliranje'),(4528,493,'_instructions_stages_3_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(4529,493,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','504'),(4530,493,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4531,493,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','316'),(4532,493,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4533,493,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','CeboVax: završna obrada za unutrašnjost na bazi pčelinjeg voska, prozračna i vodoodbojna.\r\nNanesite sloj CeboVax -a razblažen 1: 1 sa vodom, koristeći sintetički sudjer. Nanesite vosak prateći smer obrade: odmah zatim mekom krpom pređite preko površine da biste uklonili višak voska.\r\nSačekajte 10-15 minuta i ispolirajte površinu više puta prolazeći inox gletericom, pritiskajući odgovarajućom snagom.'),(4534,493,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4535,493,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details','1'),(4536,493,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(4537,493,'instructions_stages','4'),(4538,493,'_instructions_stages','field_61753c82a8577'),(4539,493,'half_section_f',''),(4540,493,'_half_section_f','field_61771b4aae9d1'),(4541,493,'half_section_s',''),(4542,493,'_half_section_s','field_61771b6cae9d2'),(4543,493,'background_image','496'),(4544,493,'_background_image','field_617722e02e7b3'),(4545,493,'main_content','<h2>Katalozi</h2>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/zidnedekoracije-new/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Cebos_S.A._CeboMarmo_Pietra_Rinascimentale.pdf\">Cebos_S.A._CeboMarmo_Pietra_Rina