on otprilike 6-8 sati, kada se CeboStyle Antico potpuno osuši, nanesite jedan sloj CeboIron-a inox gleterom, uvijek poštujući smjer prethodno dizajnirane dekoracije i pazeći da uklonite višak materijala istom lopaticom kako biste poboljšali reljefna područja.'),(4616,509,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4617,509,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','2'),(4618,509,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(4619,509,'instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','CeboIdea'),(4620,509,'_instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(4621,509,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(4622,509,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4623,509,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(4624,509,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4625,509,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','Akrilna boja na vodenoj bazi koja se zbog svoje posebne formulacije može nanositi kao ukrasni premaz za stvaranje neznatnih reljefnih efekata.'),(4626,509,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4627,509,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','1'),(4628,509,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(4629,509,'instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','CeboStyle Antico'),(4630,509,'_instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(4631,509,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(4632,509,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4633,509,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(4634,509,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_in