loga:\r\n\r\nPogodni su gipsani i građevinski premazi ili oni sa prethodnim lakiranjem, prikladno obnovljeni od prašine i oštećenja.\r\n\r\n-U prisustvu nedavno gletovanih površina, novih zidova i posebno upijajućih podloga ili podloga sa krečom, nanesite preventivni sloj CeboFix M, prozirnog akrilnog učvršćivača, razređenog 1: 1 zapreminski vodom, četkom.'),(4766,524,'_instructions_section_description','field_61753c63a8576'),(4767,524,'instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','Datalji za nanošenje boje'),(4768,524,'_instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(4769,524,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','529'),(4770,524,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4771,524,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(4772,524,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4773,524,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','Na gips, gips karton ili prethodno obojene podloge nanesite CeboFix Primo, pigmentirani akrilni prajmer, pogodan za ravne površine sa hromatskim razlikama i razlikama u upijanju. CeboFix Primo se može koristiti u beloj ili obojenoj boji, kako bi se olakšalo nanošenje i prekrivanje naknadne završne obrade, a može se nanositi valjkom ili četkom, u jednom sloju, razblaženo 20-30% zapremine vodom.'),(4774,524,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4775,524,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f','529'),(4776,524,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4777,524,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s',''),(4778,524,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4779,524,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_detail