kon sušenja prvog sloja (4-6 sati) moguće je nanijeti drugi sloj proizvoda imajući u vidu da će ovaj dalji korak učiniti boju malo intenzivnijom.'),(6542,647,'_page_main_content_description','field_6175355dc93bd'),(6543,647,'order_product_description',''),(6544,647,'_order_product_description','field_61753591c93be'),(6545,647,'instructions_section_title','Uputstvo za upotrebu'),(6546,647,'_instructions_section_title','field_61753bffa8575'),(6547,647,'instructions_section_description','Priprema podloga:\r\n\r\nProverite da li su podloge ujednačene, savršeno čiste i suve. U prisustvu nedavno gletovanih, krečnih ili upijajućih podloga, izvršite savršeno čišćenje podloge i prethodno nanesite izolacioni fiksator CeboFik M u jednom sloju, četkom, razblažen 1: 1 sa vodom.'),(6548,647,'_instructions_section_description','field_61753c63a8576'),(6549,647,'instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','FondoPlus'),(6550,647,'_instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(6551,647,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(6552,647,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(6553,647,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(6554,647,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(6555,647,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>FondoPlus</strong>\r\nAkrilni prajmer na vodenoj bazi, sa visokim prekrivanjem i belinom. Nanesite proizvod kratkodlakim valjkom, u jednom ili dva sloja, dok podloga ne bude potpuno prekrivena. Nakon što se FondoPlus osuši, nastavite sa primenom CeboTime -a.'),(6556,647,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(6557,647,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','1'),(6558,647,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(6559,647,'instructions_st