3bc'),(6621,656,'page_slider_images_2_single_slider_image','659'),(6622,656,'_page_slider_images_2_single_slider_image','field_61753531c93bc'),(6623,656,'page_slider_images','3'),(6624,656,'_page_slider_images','field_617534efc93bb'),(6625,656,'page_main_content_description','CONTRASTO BY CEBOGRANIT - FINITURE PREZIOSE &amp; EFFECTS\r\n\r\nNepravilne nijanse, emocionalne i dvobojne za enterijere istančanog i sofisticiranog ukusa.\r\n\r\nDekorativni premaz za unutrašnjost i spoljašnjost koji diše, zasnovan na akrilnim smolama i prirodnom pesku premazan pigmentima koji su visoko otporni na sunčevu svetlost i loše vremenske uslove. Primena CONTRASTO efekta omogućava dobijanje glatkih, mat površina, ali sa dvobojnim tonalitetom u određenim venama. Ekskluzivni dizajn može se prilagoditi bilo kojoj dekorativnoj potrebi, tako da može orijentisati prugu u željenom smjeru (dijagonalno,horizontalno, vodoravno). Karakterističan efekat i velika otpornost čine ga proizvodom za unutrašnju dekoraciju, pogodnim za sve površine.'),(6626,656,'_page_main_content_description','field_6175355dc93bd'),(6627,656,'order_product_description',''),(6628,656,'_order_product_description','field_61753591c93be'),(6629,656,'instructions_section_title','Uputstvo za upotrebu'),(6630,656,'_instructions_section_title','field_61753bffa8575'),(6631,656,'instructions_section_description',''),(6632,656,'_instructions_section_description','field_61753c63a8576'),(6633,656,'instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','CeboFix R'),(6634,656,'_instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(6635,656,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(6636,656,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(6637,656,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(6638,656,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(6639,656,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>CeboFix R</strong>\r\nPigmentirani, akrilni fiksator, koji sadrži sitni kvarcni pesak. Nanesite jedan ili dva sloja CeboFix R sa kratkodlakim valjkom kako biste ujednačili površinu. Kada se CeboFik R potpuno osuši, nastavite nanošenje sa CeboGranitom.'),(6640,656,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(6641,656,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','1'),(6642,656,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(6643,656,'instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','Ciklus primene - CONTRASTO efekat:'),(6644,656,'_instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(6645,656,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(6646,656,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(6647,656,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(6648,656,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(6649,656,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>Ciklus primene - CONTRASTO efekat:</strong>\r\nCeboGranit je spreman za upotrebu i mora se nanositi u dva sloja gleterom od nerđajućeg čelika. Nanesite prvi sloj CeboGranita bele boje, savršeno izglađujući površinu kako biste uklonili sve nedostatke i postigli ujednačen sloj. Kada se prvi sloj potpuno osuši (najmanje 12 sati), nanesite drugi sloj proizvoda u dve boje, prema katalogu. Prvo nanesite jednu boju, a zatim drugu paralelno i naizmenično. Uvek je preporučljivo dati prednost tamnijoj nijansi. Nastavite dugim i uskim pokretima u izabranom smeru, dovršavajući jednu stvorenu venu od početka do kraja zida. Da bi se izbegli neestetski spojevi, preporučuje se da se nastavi paralelno sa kreiranim dizajnom prethodno nanete boje. Pre potpunog sušenja, pređite po površini čistom gletericom da biste uglačali proizvod.'),(6650,656,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(6651,656,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','1'),(6652,656,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(6653,656,'instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','CeboFlow'),(6654,656,'_instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(6655,656,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(6656,656,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(6657,656,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(6658,656,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(6659,656,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>CeboFlow</strong>\r\nProvidan zaštitni proizvod na vodenoj bazi sa posebnim fluorisanim polimerima. Kada se nanese na CeboGranit, formira nevidljivu vodoodbojnu barijeru, štiteći površinu od atmosferskog zagađenja. Nanesite CeboFlow kada se CeboGranit potpuno osuši, u jednom sloju, idući odozdo prema gore kako biste izbegli kapanje.'),(6660,656,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(6661,656,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','1'),(6662,656,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(6663,656,'instructions_stages_3_instruction_label_title','CeboVitra Piu'),(6664,656,'_instructions_stages_3_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(6665,656,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(6666,656,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(6667,656,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(6668,656,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(6669,656,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>CeboVitra Piu</strong>\r\nprovidni zaštitni sjajni proizvod na vodenoj bazi, na bazi poliuretanskih smola. Nanešen na CeboGranit, čineći ga izuzetno otpornim na ogrebotine i perivim, daje okruženjima česte upotrebe (kupatila, kuhinje, stepenice, prodavnice itd.) Delikatan sjajan izgled. Nanesite CeboVitra Piu kada se CeboGranit potpuno osuši, u dva sloja valjkom sa kratkom dlakom.'),(6670,656,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(6671,656,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details','1'),(6672,656,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(6673,656,'instructions_stages','4'),(6674,656,'_instructions_stages','field_61753c82a8577'),(6675,656,'slider_or_text','1'),(6676,656,'_slider_or_text','field_6187fa34f0e09'),(6677,656,'half_section_f','<h2>Karta boja</h2>\r\nPrikazane boje su napravljene pomoću digitalnih aplikacija, stoga ih treba smatrati indikativnim i neobavezujućim. Za tačan izbor boja, pogledajte ton karte boja sa pravim proizvodom, koji su dostupni kod ovlašćenih Cebos prodavaca boja.'),(6678,656,'_half_section_f','field_61771b4aae9d1'),(6679,656,'half_section_s','<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-660\" src=\"http://localhost/zidnedekoracije-new/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/uodr6Jg.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"568\" height=\"456\" />'),(6680,656,'_half_section_s','field_61771b6cae9d2'),(6681,656,'background_image',''),(6682,656,'_background_image','field_617722e02e7b3'),(6683,656,'main_content',''),(6684,656,'_main_content','field_617724162e7b9'),(6685,656,'full_width_section','<h2>Tabala sa specifikacijom:</h2>\r\n<table border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"15%\">product</td>\r\n<td width=\"8%\">use</td>\r\n<td width=\"14%\">dilution (water)</td>\r\n<td width=\"18%\">approx. coverage</td>\r\n<td width=\"15%\">