i ujednačene po izgledu i upijanju.\r\nCeboFix R: pigmentirani i psropropusni prajmer, sadrži kvarcni prah. Može se nanositi valjkom sa  kratkom dlskom u jednom ili dva sloja do potpunog prekrivanja površine. Nakon što se CeboFix R osuši, u slučaju posebno rustikalnih ili nepravilnih podloga, nanesite CeboFondo.'),(7392,704,'_instructions_section_description','field_61753c63a8576'),(7393,704,'instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','CeboArt Pozzolano'),(7394,704,'_instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(7395,704,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7396,704,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7397,704,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7398,704,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7399,704,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>CeboArt Pozzolano</strong>\r\nDekorativni premaz, za ​​enterijere i eksterijere, paropropustan, na bazi krečnog gita, prirodan. Proizvod omogućava stvaranje različitih efekata i završnih obrada, kao što su <strong>Lamato, Lamato Lucente, Intonachino Fine ili Travertino</strong>, svi ujedinjeni neprozirnim izgledom i karakterističnim tačkama rečnog peska.'),(7400,704,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7401,704,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7402,704,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7403,704,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7404,704,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7405,704,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','<strong>CeboArt Pozzolano</strong>\r\nCiklus nanošenja Lamato efekta: na pripremljenu podlogu nanesite prvi sloj CeboArt Pozzolana gletericom od nerđajućeg čelika sa ukrštenim i nepravilnim potezima. Nakon što se osuši, nanesite drugi sloj zbijanjem proizvoda manje ili više u skladu sa željenim konačnim efektom (manje ili više zatvoren). Ako je površina previše suva, gletericu navlažite vodom.'),(7406,704,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7407,704,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7408,704,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7409,704,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7410,704,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7411,704,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_text','<strong>CeboArt Pozzolano</strong>\r\nCiklus primene Lamato Lucente efekta: na pripremljenu podlogu nanesite prvi sloj CeboArt Pozzolana kako je gore opisano. Kada se osuši, pomešajte CeboLame sa CeboArt Pozzolano i nastavite sa nanošenjem drugog sloja.'),(7412,704,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7413,704,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7414,704,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7415,704,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7416,704,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7417,704,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_text','<strong>CeboArt Pozzolano</strong>\r\nCiklus nanošenja Intonachino Fini efekat: na pripremljenu podlogu nanesite prvi sloj CeboArt Pozzolana sa gleterom od nerđajućeg čelika sa ukrštenim i nepravilnim potezima. Nakon što se osuši, nanesite drugi sloj gleterom od nerđajućeg čelika i nakon što je proizvod još mokar, kružnim pokretima pređite preko površine finim sunđerastim plovkom (A/58 ili A/59) dimenzija 24 × 12 ili 12 × 12 centimetara. Ako je podloga previše suva, navlažite plovak vodom.'),(7418,704,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7419,704,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_4_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7420,704,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_4_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7421,704,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_4_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7422,704,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_4_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7423,704,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_4_add_instruction_text','<strong>CeboArt Pozzolano</strong>\r\nCiklus nanošenja efekta sedre: nanesite CeboArt Pozzolano gleterom od nerđajućeg čelika u homogenoj debljini od 1-2 mm. Dok je proizvod još mokar, obradite površinu posebnim CeboSign alatom (A / 35) od 12 × 12 cm da biste ponovo stvorili karakteristične žile sedre. Da biste postigli prirodniji efekat, nastavite sa obradom na nepravilan način, izbegavajući ponavljanje dizajna. Pre potpunog sušenja proizvoda, gletujte površinu gleterom, lagano pritiskajući podignute delove. Ako je proizvod previše suv, gletericu navlažite vodom.'),(7424,704,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_4_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7425,704,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','5'),(7426,704,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(7427,704,'instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','CeboArt CalceFine'),(7428,704,'_instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(7429,704,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7430,704,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7431,704,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7432,704,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7433,704,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>CeboArt CalceFine</strong>\r\nDekorativni premaz, za ​​enterijere i eksterijere, prozračan, na bazi krečnog gita, prirodan. Proizvod vam omogućava da kreirate elegantne završne obrade sa savršeno neprozirnim izgledom, kao što su Levigato ili Levigato Lucente.'),(7434,704,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7435,704,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7436,704,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7437,704,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7438,704,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7439,704,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','<strong>CeboArt CalceFine</strong>\r\nCiklus nanošenja Levigato efekta: na pripremljenu i potpuno suvu podlogu nanesite prvi sloj CalceFine -a sa gleterom od nerđajućeg čelika sa ukrštenim i nepravilnim gletericama. Nakon sušenja nanesite drugi sloj sabijanjem proizvoda.'),(7440,704,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7441,704,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7442,704,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7443,704,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7444,704,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7445,704,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_text','<strong>CeboArt CalceFine</strong>\r\nCiklus nanošenja za efekat Levigato Lucente: na pripremljenu i potpuno suvu podlogu nanesite prvi sloj CalceFine -a kako je gore opisano. Kada se osuši, pomešajte CeboLame sa CeboArt CalceFine i nastavite sa nanošenjem drugog sloja sabijanjem proizvoda.\r\nCeboSil: paropropusna i vodoodbojna akril-siloksanska zaštitna završna obrada sa mat i baršunastim dodirom. Proizvod razblažite vodom u odnosu 1: 1. CeboSil se nanosi u jednom nanosu sintetičkim sunđerom, nastavljajući odozdo prema gore kako bi se izbjeglo kapanje\r\n'),(7446,704,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7447,704,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7448,704,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7449,704,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7450,704,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7451,704,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_text','CeboLame: specijalni aditiv u pahuljicama na bazi prirodnog liskuna koji se dodaje u CeboArt Pozzolano ili CeboArt CalceFine stvara elegantne svetlosne tačke u finišu. CeboLame je dostupan u srebrnim i zlatnim nijansama u pakovanjima od 25 ml i 100 ml za upotrebu u sledećim dozama:\r\n1 x 100 ml in 20 kg tin\r\n1 x 25 ml in 5 kg tin.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-706\" src=\"http://localhost/zidnedekoracije-new/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Tabella-Applicativa_sito_EN-1-1024x331.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"331\" />\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/h95bKATgIGM\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Pogledajte video sa detaljima</a>'),(7452,704,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7453,704,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','4'),(7454,704,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(7455,704,'instructions_stages','2'),(7456,704,'_instructions_stages','field_61753c82a857