','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7533,708,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','1'),(7534,708,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(7535,708,'instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','Ciklus primene CeboArt Stucco'),(7536,708,'_instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(7537,708,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7538,708,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7539,708,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7540,708,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7541,708,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>Ciklus primene CeboArt Stucco</strong>\r\nNanesite CeboArt Stucco u tri sloja gleterom od nerđajućeg čelika. Na pripremljenu i suvu površinu nanesite dovoljnu količinu proizvoda da dobijete glatki sloj. Kada se prvi sloj potpuno osuši (nakon otprilike 6-8 sati), drugi sloj nanesite lopaticom ili sečivom od nerđajućeg čelika da biste stvorili željenu dekoraciju, a zatim savršeno zagladite površinu. U treći sloj nanesite malu količinu proizvoda, blago omekšanu, uklanjajući višak; pre nego što se proizvod potpuno osuši, ispolirajte celu površinu istom lopaticom.'),(7542,708,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7543,708,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','1'),(7544,708,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(7545,708,'instructions_stages_3_instruction_label_title','CeboArt Marmorino'),(7546,708,'_instructions_stages_3_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(7547,708,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7548,708,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7549,708,'instructions_stages_3