ebra, bakra i bronze, te bezbroj primenjivih efekata ističu baš ona pogodna dekorativna rešenja za personalizovanje modernih prostora sa avanturističkim dizajnom.\r\n\r\nOni takođe savršeno odgovaraju prilagođavanju prostora sa starinskim nameštajem.\r\n\r\n- Nanesite MARCOPOLO na podlogu prethodno pripremljenu pomoću DECORFOND.\r\n\r\nMARCOPOLO omogućava izvođenje sledećih efekata:\r\n\r\nEFEKAT VODOPADA\r\nEFEKAT RIGATO\r\nEFEKAT TRAMATO'),(11310,1060,'_page_main_content_description','field_6175355dc93bd'),(11311,1060,'order_product_description',''),(11312,1060,'_order_product_description','field_61753591c93be'),(11313,1060,'instructions_section_title','Različiti efekti tehnike Marcopolo'),(11314,1060,'_instructions_section_title','field_61753bffa8575'),(11315,1060,'instructions_section_description',''),(11316,1060,'_instructions_section_description','field_61753c63a8576'),(11317,1060,'instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','Dekorativni finiš za enterijere, s efektom sirovog metala'),(11318,1060,'_instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(11319,1060,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','1066'),(11320,1060,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(11321,1060,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(11322,1060,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(11323,1060,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text',''),(11324,1060,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(11325,1060,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','1'),(11326,1060,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(11327,1060,'instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','Efekat Vodopada'),(11328,1060,'_instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(11329,1060,'instruct