površina s finim metalik efektom, pogodnih za elegantan, klasičan i moderan ambijent.\r\n\r\nZahvaljujući posebno lakoj primeni, pomoću MARCOPOLO LUXURY mogu da se kreiraju brojni dekorativni efekti, igre svetlosti i refleksi za ispunjenje svih estetskih želja.\r\n\r\nKarakterističan stil ovog sredstva za završnu obradu pogoduje prostorima s jednostavnom, ali krajnje rafiniranom atmosferom.\r\n\r\nOn ambijentima daje izražajnost i objedinjuje savremeni prilaz elementima sa šarmom starine u sebi.\r\n\r\n- Nanesite MARCOPOLO na podlogu prethodno pripremljenu pomoću DECORFOND\r\n\r\nMARCOPOLO LUXURY omogućava izvođenje sledećih efekata:\r\n\r\nEFEKAT REAL\r\nEFEKAT PRUGA\r\nEFEKAT ORIJENT'),(11433,1071,'_page_main_content_description','field_6175355dc93bd'),(11434,1071,'order_product_description',''),(11435,1071,'_order_product_description','field_61753591c93be'),(11436,1071,'instructions_section_title','Različiti efekti tehnike Marcopolo Luxury'),(11437,1071,'_instructions_section_title','field_61753bffa8575'),(11438,1071,'instructions_section_description',''),(11439,1071,'_instructions_section_description','field_61753c63a8576'),(11440,1071,'instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','Fino-metalik rafinirana tekstura'),(11441,1071,'_instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(11442,1071,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','1081'),(11443,1071,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(11444,1071,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(11445,1071,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(11446,1071,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text',''),(11447,1071,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(11448,1071,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','1'),(11449,1071,'_instructions_stage