đa takođe izložene u vlažnom okruženju ili u industrijskoj ili morskoj atmosferi. Za poboljšanje otpornosti na ogrebotine moguće je prebojati UNIMARC FINITURA LEGNO s. 318 sjajna ili satenska, ili UNIMARC FINITURA CERATA bezbojna 3120300. Približni prinos: 8-10 m2 / l po sloju. Broj slojeva: 1-2. Alati: četka, valjak, sprej i Airless. Razblaživanje: sa Vhite Spirit 5200010 ili Dil. Sintetički 5210011 četkom / valjkom na 0-3% raspršivanjem mak 8%.'),(12700,1208,'_page_main_content_description','field_6175355dc93bd'),(12701,1208,'order_product_description',''),(12702,1208,'_order_product_description','field_61753591c93be'),(12703,1208,'instructions_section_title',''),(12704,1208,'_instructions_section_title','field_61753bffa8575'),(12705,1208,'instructions_section_description',''),(12706,1208,'_instructions_section_description','field_61753c63a8576'),(12707,1208,'instructions_stages',''),(12708,1208,'_instructions_stages','field_61753c82a8577'),(12709,1208,'slider_or_text','1'),(12710,1208,'_slider_or_text','field_6187fa34f0e09'),(12711,1208,'half_section_f',''),(12712,1208,'_half_section_f','field_61771b4aae9d1'),(12713,1208,'half_section_s',''),(12714,1208,'_half_section_s','field_61771b6cae9d2'),(12715,1208,'background_image',''),(12716,1208,'_background_image','field_617722e02e7b3'),(12717,1208,'main_content',''),(12718,1208,'_main_content','field_617724162e7b9'),(12719,1208,'full_width_section',''),(12720,1208,'_full_width_section','field_6177246f65aab'),(12721,1208,'_yoast_wpseo_primary_kategorija-proizvoda','13'),(12722,1208,'_yoast_wpseo_estimated-reading-time-minutes',''),(12723,1211,'_wp_attached_file','2021/11/IMG_8218.jpg'),(12724,1211,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:2048;s:6:\"height\";i:2048;s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"2021/11/IMG_8218.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:5:{s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"IMG_8218-300x300.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:300;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:5:\"large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:22:\"IMG_82